Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.93,0:00:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶的日记怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  这上面写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}（小瑛和一叶  有抱错的可能）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.49,0:00:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都跟你说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你说不用去找了…
